Product Offerings


Product Offerings
Full Spectrum. Flexible Structures. Large Hold Positions.


Ares Capital Corporation ("Ares Capital" or "ARCC") focuses on event-driven financings such as buyouts, acquisitions, recapitalizations, restructurings and rescue financing. We also provide growth capital and general refinancings.
Across all of our products, Ares Capital seeks to:

Invest across the entire capital structure in both debt and equity securities
Utilize our flexible investment mandate in order to customize financing solutions for each deal
Provide consistent capital throughout all segments of market cycles

We provide capital at all levels of the balance sheet and for a variety of corporate finance solutions.






